{"tid":797154,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇經濟學家分析下其實大家樂個南冰魚柳係點樣賺錢","createTime":"2018-08-28T09:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T03:24:34.000Z","uid":38189,"like":35,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"78151633f46ce614649cee0aa0e3ec0409e67292","tid":797154,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/174309_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F174309_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd7ea025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n塊魚柳又香又脆又新鮮肯定係靚野<br />\n一塊我計佢15蚊(可能批發價平d減$2)<br />\n塊多士3蚊烘底再加2蚊=5，<br />\n獨立包裝牛油起碼$1.5<br />\n兩隻蛋每隻3蚊=6<br />\n仲有杯醒神熱飲=8蚊<br />\n15-2+5+1.5+6+8=42.5蚊<br />\n加埋嗰啲燈油火蠟人工 咁咪蝕到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家多啲幫襯呢d良心企業，唔好幫襯啲濕鳩小店，因為大家樂嘅鋪租遠遠高於嗰啲小店。<br />\n<br />\n利申：非打手 有感而發"},{"pid":"d2ad86b5fcc1387e7f4734d3ef5f547e1a27ffb2","tid":797154,"uid":37733,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"蝕住做<br />\n志在回饋社會賺商譽"},{"pid":"dcc59eb3f5a3b70c9b615fecb85bd79750d12768","tid":797154,"uid":38189,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"d2ad86b5fcc1387e7f4734d3ef5f547e1a27ffb2","tid":797154,"uid":37733,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"蝕住做<br />\n志在回饋社會賺商譽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"有時見到d廢青出言侮辱大家樂真係會心痛"},{"pid":"d334b14a95103fc5363843be0c21922c710d000b","tid":797154,"uid":78971,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"但求打個和架咋<br />\n<br />\n做過大家樂清潔"},{"pid":"3c7675b13bfeab20ec8a6e89bae9fd049ccd2be1","tid":797154,"uid":199211,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"我話你知蝕到仆街<br />\n搭飛機去南極都幾萬<br />\n都唔計請漁夫 租破冰船 嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/face